page.title: 12DOG KENNELS
page.content:
{TRADE {DOG KENNELS AT WELL KNOWE Well Knowe Kennels are owned by Miss Pat Jones. She has run the kennels for 18 years. The name Well Knowe comes from the fact that there was a well on the hill where the kennels are. There are at least 12 different species of dog at the kennels. They are fed on Pedigree Chum, raw mince and biscuits. The kennels are cleaned out 3 or 4 times a day and the dogs are exercised twice a day. Miss Jones is well known at dog shows. She is best known for her bearded collie dogs.
